      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/d576e47ec29592a74d7f18040459665c_7355264158400820181.png",
                "id": "talent19704",
                "key": "Fight Club Legend ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fight Club Legend "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Geo DMG</span>. Summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ushi</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superlative Superstrength</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Superlative Superstrength</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached uses a Charged Attack:</span> Deal +1 DMG. If the Usage(s) are no less than 2, expend 1 less <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Unaligned Element</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/c75ed9237fb342dae8cd65729ddc0bba_7571236184714692709.png",
                "id": "talent49796",
                "key": "Masatsu Zetsugi: Akaushi Burst! ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Masatsu Zetsugi: Akaushi Burst! "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Raging Oni King</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Raging Oni King</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>The character to which this is attached has their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attacks</span> deal +1 DMG, and their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character to which this is attached uses a Normal Attack:</span> Gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superlative Superstrength</span>. (Once per Round)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Superlative Superstrength</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached uses a Charged Attack:</span> Deal +1 DMG. If the Usage(s) are no less than 2, expend 1 less <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Unaligned Element</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/d5b0f60e30da0341b4165d1a76b3c73b_363057504685643345.png",
                "id": "talent24655",
                "key": "Royal Descent: Behold, Itto the Evil! ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Royal Descent: Behold, Itto the Evil! "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your active character takes DMG</span>: Decrease DMG taken by 1.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span>. When the Usage is depleted, this card will not be discarded.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Can be triggered once while this Summon is present:</span> When your active character takes DMG, Arataki Itto gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superlative Superstrength</span>.</p><p>End Phase: Discard this card, deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Superlative Superstrength</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached uses a Charged Attack:</span> Deal +1 DMG. If the Usage(s) are no less than 2, expend 1 less <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Unaligned Element</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3549277289296865062.png",
                "id": "talent91859",
                "key": "Ushi",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/35428890/ea059a3f7bee2dea6bcee851752339c3_7452437415273984823.png",
                "title": "Ushi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_5698420689095315495.png",
                "id": "talent43042",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Unaligned Element</span></strong></p><p>You may use Elemental Dice of any element to pay this type of cost.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.<br><br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_725159971590464858.png",
                "id": "talent37624",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
